  "instructions": [
    "Heat the score-fat in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add the gochujang, soy sauce, and rice vinegar, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cubed tofu and cook until it is coated in the sauce.",
    "Crumble the feta cheese into the pot and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped green onions and serve hot."
